<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CHEESE AND WINE APPRECIATION SOCIETY!</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Love cheese? Love wine? Join Butler cheese and wine appreciation society!!!!&nbsp;</strong><strong>Whether you're wine mad or a complete novice in wine tasting, or simply enjoy socialising with good friends over a glass of wine and cheese, join Butler Wine appreciation society!!</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong><strong>When </strong></strong>&nbsp;A few evenings throughout the term! Facebook events and posters round college will keep you updated when.</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><strong><strong>Where?</strong></strong>&nbsp;Mainly in college but will be livers out cheese and wine too for those further away</span></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><strong><strong>How much?&nbsp;</strong></strong>Roughly &pound;5 a meeting for as much wine and cheese you can drink and eat!</span></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<strong>Possible ideas for the year: </strong>Themed wine nights, introduction of chutney and grapes and chilled out music and voting of the best wines each meeting.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal"><strong>There is something for everyone whether you're coming for pre drinks or &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;just a chilled out evening, join us!!!!!!</strong></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">Please join our Facebook page to keep up with all the latest events and news</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/176753342412922/?fref=ts">https://www.facebook.com/groups/176753342412922/?fref=ts</a></p><p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/176753342412922/?fref=ts">&nbsp;</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p>